  "title": "Packer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br>\n•⁠ ⁠Pack goods according to company’s standards and guidelines<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Ensure items are properly labelled and securely packaged<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Inspect products for defects or damage before packing<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Maintain a clean and organized packing area<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Follow safety protocols to ensure a safe working environment<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Collaborate with team members to meet packing deadlines</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong><br>\n•⁠ ⁠Previous experience in a packing or similar role is preferred but not required<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Attention to detail and high level of accuracy<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Ability to work independently and as part of a team<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Good physical condition with the ability to stand, bend, and lift items as needed<br>\n•⁠ ⁠Positive attitude and reliable work ethic</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
